[[["nummod", "acl", "dobj", "det", "compound"], "Unit 3  Inventing a Better World."], [["advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "det", "amod", "nsubj", "cop", "det", "nmod", "case", "dep", "amod", "dep", "acl", "compound:prt", "nmod", "case", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "nmod:poss", "amod"], "As an old saying goes, Necessity is the mother of invention. Many times, people come up with ideas to meet their own needs."], [["advmod", "nsubj", "det", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "aux", "xcomp", "amod", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "dobj", "nmod:poss", "nmod", "case"], "Later, the solutions to their problems may become great inventions that change our way of life."], [["nsubj", "det", "nummod", "advmod", "aux", "advmod", "dobj", "det"], "The two examples below will perfectly explain this point."], [["nsubj", "compound", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "cop", "det", "amod", "amod", "dobj", "nmod:poss", "amod", "advcl", "advmod", "nsubj", "cop", "det", "amod", "compound"], "Teng Hung-chi, who is a famous Taiwanese inventor, created his first invention when he was a vocational school student."], [["nmod", "case", "det", "nsubj", "aux", "nmod", "case", "det", "compound"], "At that time, he was working as a factory mechanic."], [["nmod:tmod", "nummod", "nsubj", "aux", "dobj", "det", "nmod", "case", "det"], "One day, he was using the restroom in the factory."], [["nsubj", "nmod:poss", "cop", "nmod", "case", "dep", "parataxis", "nsubj", "aux", "neg", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "det"], "His hands were dirty from work, so he did not want to touch the faucet."], [["nsubj", "advmod", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "det", "amod", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "aux", "advmod", "advcl", "mark", "auxpass"], "He then hoped to design a special faucet which could run automatically without being touched."], [["nsubj", "xcomp", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "det", "nmod", "case"], "Teng worked hard to put this idea into practice."], [["advmod", "case", "nsubj", "dobj", "det", "acl:relcl", "nsubjpass", "auxpass", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "amod"], "Before long, he invented a faucet that was controlled by a built-in sensing device."], [["nmod", "case", "det", "nsubj", "cop", "advmod"], "At the time, he was only seventeen."], [["nsubj", "det", "amod", "advmod", "dobj", "det", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "nmod", "case", "dep", "compound"], "This young inventor later sold the rights to his invention for NT$1.5 million."], [["nmod", "case", "nsubj", "aux", "dobj", "amod", "amod", "amod"], "Since then, Teng has created many other useful inventions."], [["nsubj", "aux", "advmod", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "det", "compound", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "cop", "det", "amod", "nmod", "case"], "He has also represented Taiwan at the iENA exhibition, which is an international exhibition in Germany."], [["nsubj", "aux", "dobj", "amod", "advmod", "dobj", "amod"], "He has won first prize there many times."], [["nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "amod", "amod", "nsubj", "aux", "dep", "nmod", "case", "compound"], "For his many brilliant inventions, Teng has become known as Taiwans Edison."], [["nsubj", "det", "amod", "amod", "amod", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "cop", "det", "amod"], "The other wonderful modern invention that came from a simple need is the Post-it note."], [["nsubj", "cop", "neg", "advcl", "case"], "Post-it was not successful at first."], [["nmod", "case", "nsubj", "cop", "det", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod"], "In fact, it was the result of a failed experiment."], [["nsubj", "compound", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "cop", "nmod", "case", "det", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "aux", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "det", "amod"], "Spencer Silver, who was one of the inventors of the Post-it note, had tried to invent a strong glue."], [["advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "nmod", "case", "amod", "nsubj", "det", "neg", "dobj", "nmod:poss", "amod", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "ccomp", "compound:prt", "xcomp", "mark", "cop", "advmod"], "Although he experimented with different chemicals, the results never met his expectationsXthe glue that he made turned out to be very weak."], [["nsubj", "xcomp", "advmod"], "He wasnt disappointed, though."], [["advmod", "nsubj", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "nmod:poss", "nmod", "case", "det", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "aux", "neg"], "Instead, he tried to convince his co-workers of the usefulness of the weak glue, but they did not listen."], [["advmod", "nsubj", "compound", "amod", "dobj", "amod"], "However, Silvers weak glue drew someones attention."], [["advcl", "advmod", "nsubj", "compound", "compound", "compound", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "compound", "nsubj", "nmod:poss", "compound:prt", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "compound", "dep", "cc", "conj", "dep", "nsubj", "advmod", "dobj"], "When Silvers co-worker Art Fry sang hymns during church services, his bookmarks fell out of his hymn book again and again, which really frustrated him."], [["nmod:tmod", "nummod", "nsubj", "nmod", "case", "ccomp", "mark", "csubj", "dobj", "compound", "amod", "nmod", "case", "det", "nmod", "case", "aux", "cop", "xcomp", "mark", "ccomp", "nsubj", "dobj", "det", "amod", "advcl", "mark", "dobj", "det"], "One day, it occurred to him that using Silvers weak glue on a piece of paper might be able to help him mark the right page without damaging the book."], [["advmod", "nsubj", "nmod", "case", "det", "cc", "conj", "dobj", "nmod:poss", "nmod", "case", "nmod", "case", "det"], "Then, he returned to the office and shared his thought with others in the company."], [["nsubjpass", "det", "amod", "auxpass", "nmod", "case", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "aux", "advmod", "case", "nmod", "case", "det"], "The Post-it note was born in 1980, and it has since successfully spread around the world."], [["advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "aux", "nsubj", "amod", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "amod"], "As you can see, excellent inventors get ideas from their own experiences."], [["nsubj", "amod", "nsubj", "dobj", "det", "dep", "xcomp", "mark", "nmod", "case", "det", "acl", "mark", "nmod", "case"], "Next time you have a problem, try to think of a way to deal with it."], [["advmod", "nsubj", "aux", "advmod", "xcomp", "det", "amod", "advmod"], "Perhaps you will also become a great inventor someday."]]